Pre-Game Insights: Jasprit Bumrah is set to make his return to the field after a long injury lay-off.
Bumrah will lead the team during the upcoming T20I series against Ireland, starting with the first match on Friday.
The Indian team made its touchdown in Ireland on Tuesday and wasted little time in hitting the ground a day later.
Bumrah was seen bowling at full tilt to the Indian batters in the nets, indicating his recovery and readiness for the match.
The India squad also includes pacer Prasidh Krishna, who is making a comeback after a lengthy injury lay-off due to a lumbar stress fracture.
